content_html:
The number of people who died during the Gen-Z protests has reached 73. Police Spokesperson (DIG) Vinod Ghimire confirmed this number to the media. The deaths occurred during protests that took place on the 23rd and 24th of Bhadau.

Police Personnel Among the Deceased
